<section class="block">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="meetj reveal">
      <div class="meetj-img">
        <img src="/jackson-install-square.webp" width="900" height="900" loading="lazy" alt="A Bay City Blinds installer fitting a roller shutter at a Geelong home" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Who you're dealing with</p>
        <h2>Not a franchise. Just Jackson &amp; his team.</h2>
        <p>Bay City Blinds isn't a franchise. Jackson and his installers <b>are</b> the business — the same local faces at your measure, your install, and any time you need a hand down the track.</p>
        <ul class="meetj-list">
          <li>
            <span class="li-ic2"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg></span>
            <div><b>Police &amp; security checked</b><span>Jackson and every installer, so you always know who's in your home.</span></div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="li-ic2"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l2.9 6.3 6.9.6-5.2 4.6 1.6 6.8L12 17.3 5.8 20.9l1.6-6.8L2.2 8.9l6.9-.6z"/></svg></span>
            <div><b>Years of 5-star reviews</b><span>A reputation built job by job, right across greater Geelong.</span></div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="li-ic2"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 11l9-8 9 8"/><path d="M5 10v10h14V10"/></svg></span>
            <div><b>A local with skin in the game</b><span>A Geelong local dedicated to the best value workmanship and materials.</span></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="meetj-cta">
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/about">Meet Jackson →</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg" href="/about#team">Meet the team</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
